window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Revenge was the sort of temptation a master assassin would never succumb to. But when one decides to make an exception things can get </b><b><i>very</i></b><b> ugly.</b></p> <p>Many years had elapsed since Bawb ascended to the ranks of the elite Master Ghalian, but his upward climb was not yet complete. A mysterious hint of greater things to come lingered, but despite his best efforts and all manner of challenges, he was still in the dark as to what exactly that might be.</p> <p>There was something about a dragon. Something about a mage. But what that meant he had no idea. Little did he know, if he did find out, it would change his life forever.</p>"; 
